<P>
Profile 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA101589-0044 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 120712 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
October 15, 1989, Sunday, Valley Edition 
</P>
