HURRICANE AID 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Following the havoc of Hurricane Hugo, has any country offered any aid or 
assistance to the U.S., particularly Canada, Mexico, the Soviet Union, Japan or 
Israel? I have neither read nor heard of any. 
</P>
<P>
C.E. O'HARE 
</P>
<P>
Pasadena 
</P>
