<HEADLINE>
<P>
A TEST FOR QUALITY MANUFACTURE OF PLIERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
High-precision cutting pliers are finished so they'll meet at the point. Hold a 
good pair of diagonal cutters up to the light, says Cooper'Tools, and you 
should see a line of light that grows wider toward the back of the cutting 
edges. 
</P>
