<HEADLINE>
<P>
THE WEEK AHEAD: A LOOK AT UPCOMING EVENTS IN LOS ANGELES COUNTY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SECESSION HEARING: A public hearing is scheduled for Wednesday night at an 
Arcadia junior high school on the push by some Sierra Madre parents to secede 
from the Pasadena school district and join the more affluent Arcadia school 
district. 
</P>
