<HEADLINE>
<P>
SPAIN SEIZES DRUG SUSPECTS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
BARCELONA, Spain 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Police said Saturday that they had arrested three Dutchmen and three Spaniards 
on suspicion of forming a cocaine-trafficking ring. Police detained the six in 
Barcelona last week in a raid during which they also seized 15 pounds of 
cocaine. 
</P>
</TEXT>
