WAYNE GRETZKY IN 1989:Oct. 8; Detroit vs. Kings at Forum 
</P>
<P>
Assists with Mikael Lindholm on Bob Kudelski's goal in first period 
</P>
<P>
Goaltender: Tim Cheveldae. 
</P>
<P>
</P>
<P>
POINT NO.:1,842 
