<HEADLINE>
<P>
HOUSING PROJECT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
On the front page of your Orange County Edition (Oct. 6), there was a story on 
a housing project for low-income families to be built by a coalition of Habitat 
for Humanity, the Fieldstone Co. and Rancho Santa Margarita. 
</P>
<P>
While the great bulk of information you conveyed was correct, there was one 
significant error. Your article stated that this project was basically my idea. 
While I would like to take credit for it, it was the brainchild of Dave 
Langlois, one of our corporate directors and manager of our Orange County 
division. 
</P>
<P>
