<P>
Pay Telephones -- Long Beach Councilman Wallace Edgerton has proposed a study 
on restricting incoming calls on certain pay telephones to try to put a crimp 
in drug deals. A headline in the Times Long Beach section Thursday incorrectly 
described the type of calls that would be restricted. 
</P>
